    <body xml:space="preserve"><div n="61" type="kitchenTip" xml:id="wo1a.61" xml:lang="de-x-enh"> <title key="Buck liver, served cold">Ain Richt von pockleber etc.</title> <instruction><ingredient commodity="Q1470283" en="liver">Pocks leber</ingredient> kalt mit den <ingredient commodity="Q9377" en="kidney">nieren</ingredient> gesnitten zuo scheiben</instruction> vnd <alternative reason="serving"> gemacht oder jn ainem <ingredient commodity="Q15645384" en="wheat">weissen</ingredient> <ingredient commodity="Q21546392" en="garlic">knoblauch</ingredient></alternative> <ab n="1" subtype="subrecipe" type="kitchenTip" xml:id="wo1a.61.sub.1" xml:lang="de-x-enh"><servingTip><opener>Item</opener> <title key=""><ingredient commodity="Q14566073" en="mutton">schaeffens flaesch</ingredient> mit <ingredient commodity="Q25284" en="parsley">petersil</ingredient></title> vnd mit der <ingredient commodity="Q42527" en="spice">wurcz</ingredient></servingTip></ab> <ab n="2" subtype="subrecipe" type="kitchenTip" xml:id="wo1a.61.sub.2" xml:lang="de-x-enh">	<servingTip><opener>Item</opener> <title key=""><ingredient commodity="Q7230136" en="pork loin">sweinen ruck</ingredient> mit jungem <ingredient commodity="Q3406628" en="onion">zwifel</ingredient></title></servingTip> <closer>etc.</closer></ab></div></body>
